SUMMARY:GTM IN THE AI ERA
DESCRIPTION:‚ÄãGTM in the AI Era: People\, Stack\, and What‚Äôs Actually Working \n‚ÄãJoin us at AI House for an off-the-record style\, high-signal conversation on how AI is reshaping go-to-market. This is a moderated panel\, built for real dialogue and practical takeaways\, not pitches or demos. \n‚ÄãWe‚Äôll unpack three angles leaders are navigating right now: \n‚ÄãPeople & AI: hiring trends\, AI literacy\, and recruiting impact \n‚ÄãGTM Foundations + Tech Stack: what must be true before layering AI into your GTM motion \n‚ÄãMarket Trends & Lessons Learned: what‚Äôs working\, what isn‚Äôt\, and where teams are getting surprised \n‚ÄãDate: March 18\nTime: 4:30‚Äì6:30 PM (networking before and after the panel)\nLocation: AI House\nFormat: 35‚Äì45 minute moderated panel + networking \n‚ÄãWho it‚Äôs for: CROs\, VPs/Directors of Sales\, Growth leaders\, Founders\, and select Investors. \n‚ÄãCapacity is limited. If this is your world\, you‚Äôll leave with sharper perspective\, clearer language\, and a more grounded view of what ‚ÄúAI-ready GTM‚Äù actually looks like.
URL:https://www.geekwire.com/calendar-event/gtm-in-the-ai-era/
LOCATION:AI House\, 2801 Alaskan Wy\, Seattle\, WA\, 98121
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://cdn.geekwire.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Screenshot-2026-02-26-104022.png
END:VEVENT
