SUMMARY:AI Madness: 16 Tools. One Champion. North Sound Decides.
DESCRIPTION:Which AI tools are actually worth your time ‚Äî and which ones are all hype? \n‚ÄãWe‚Äôre settling it the only way that makes sense in March: a bracket-style showdown. 16 AI tools go head-to-head across four categories. You debate. You vote. One champion gets crowned. \n‚ÄãWhether you‚Äôre a founder who lives in ChatGPT\, a small business owner who just started using Canva‚Äôs AI features\, or someone who keeps hearing about AI but hasn‚Äôt found the right entry point ‚Äî this is your night. \n‚ÄãüìçHemlock State Brewing Co.\n‚ÄãüìÖThurs\, Mar 19\n‚Äã‚è∞5:00‚Äì7:30 PM \n‚ÄãTHE BRACKET\n‚ÄãüßÝTHE BRAINS(AI Assistants) ChatGPT vs Perplexity | Claude vs Gemini\n‚Äãüé®THE CREATIVES(Content & Design) Canva Magic Studio vs Adobe Firefly | Midjourney vs DALL¬∑E 3\n‚Äã‚öôÔ∏èTHE OPERATORS(Productivity & Business) Microsoft Copilot vs Grammarly | Notion AI vs Zapier AI\n‚Äãüî¨THE SPECIALISTS(Niche & Emerging) GitHub Copilot vs Otter.ai | Runway vs Descript \n‚ÄãAGENDA\n‚Äã*5:00 PM ‚Äì Open Networking + Fill Out Your Bracket Prediction Sheet\n‚Äã*5:30 PM ‚Äì Welcome & Rules\n‚Äã*5:40 PM ‚Äì Round of 16: Lightning Pitches + Crowd Votes\n‚Äã*6:05 PM ‚Äì Elite 8: Table Debates (Small Group Rounds)\n‚Äã*6:25 PM ‚Äì Final 4: Full Room Showdown\n‚Äã*6:40 PM ‚Äì Championship + Open Discussion\n‚Äã*7:00 PM ‚Äì Networking Wind-Down \n‚ÄãWHO THIS IS FOR\n*‚ÄãSmall business owners and entrepreneurs\n‚Äã*Tech professionals\, contractors\, and startup founders\n‚Äã*Anyone curious about AI tools ‚Äî no technical or hooper background needed \n‚ÄãWHAT YOU‚ÄôLL WALK AWAY WITH\n*‚ÄãA clear picture of which AI tools are worth trying for YOUR work\n‚Äã*Real-world tips from people actually using these tools daily\n‚Äã*A network of fellow innovators across the North Sound\n‚Äã*Bragging rights if your bracket predictions hold up \n‚ÄãNo slides. No lectures. Just a bracket\, good drinks\, and real conversation about what‚Äôs working with AI. \n‚ÄãDrinks and connections await ‚Äî RSVP now (attendance is FREE)! \n‚ÄãAdam & Ryan
URL:https://www.geekwire.com/calendar-event/ai-madness-16-tools-one-champion-north-sound-decides/
LOCATION:Hemlock State Brewing Co.\, 23601 56th Ave W Suite 400\, Mountlake Terrace\, 98043\, United States
CATEGORIES:Artificial Intelligence,Games,Geek Life,Meetups,Startups
