SUMMARY:Equitable AI For Outcomes Virtual Convening
DESCRIPTION:Project Evident is hosting Equitable AI for Outcomes: Moving from Principles to Practice\, a free virtual convening on March 25\, 2026. The event will explore how organizations can adopt AI responsibly while centering equity and measurable outcomes. Participants will hear from experts\, nonprofit leaders\, and innovators working at the intersection of AI and social impact. \nThis one-day virtual convening brings organizations together to explore what equitable AI adoption looks like in real-world practice. \nCentered on Project Evident‚Äôs new Equitable AI Adoption framework‚Äîdeveloped in partnership with 34 nonprofit practitioners\, district leaders\, and subject matter experts‚Äîthis virtual convening will showcase how organizations are navigating governance\, supporting staff\, and measuring impact as they integrate AI into their work.
