SUMMARY:Insforge x Qoder AI Agent Hackathon ‚Äì $3\,000 Cash Prize
DESCRIPTION:Build the next generation of autonomous AI agents ‚Äî together. \n‚Äãüåç What‚Äôs This About?\n‚ÄãAI isn‚Äôt just the future ‚Äî it‚Äôs happening now. Join a community of mission-driven developers\, designers\, and builders for a one-day\, in-person hackathon focused on building autonomous AI agents and AI-powered applications that solve real-world problems. \n‚ÄãThis hackathon centers around the powerful combination of Qoder and Insforge\, providing a full end-to-end AI-native development stack: \n‚ÄãQoder ‚Äî An Agentic IDE designed for real software development. It transforms how AI understands code; beyond snippets\, it grasps your entire architecture\, dependencies\, and patterns. \n‚ÄãInsforge ‚Äî An Agent-native Backend Platform that lets your coding agents build and run the backend for you. Add Auth\, DB\, Storage\, and Serverless functions to your app in seconds. \n‚ÄãTogether\, these platforms enable a new way of building software: AI agents that don‚Äôt just write code\, but also test it\, connect it to real backends\, and ship production-ready systems. \n‚ÄãüéØ Agenda\n‚Äã09:00 AM ‚Äì Doors Open & Check-In \n‚Äã09:30 AM ‚Äì Opening & Platform Demos (Qoder & Insforge) \n‚Äã09:50 AM ‚Äì Team Formation & Ideation (Teams may also be formed in advance through our Discord channel.) \n‚Äã10:00 AM ‚Äì Hacking Begins üöÄ \n‚Äã12:00 PM ‚Äì Lunch Served üçï \n‚Äã04:00 PM ‚Äì Project Submission Deadline ‚è≥ \n‚Äã04:15 PM ‚Äì Pitches & Demo Showcase \n‚Äã05:15 PM ‚Äì Judging & Networking \n‚Äã05:45 PM ‚Äì Awards Ceremony üèÜ \n‚Äã06:00 PM ‚Äì Event Concludes \n‚ÄãüèÜ Prizes ‚Äî $3\,000 Total Pool\n‚Äãü•á 1st Place ‚Äì $1\,000 \n‚Äãü•à 2nd Place ‚Äì $800 \n‚Äãü•â 3rd Place ‚Äì $500 \n‚Äãüß™ Best Use of Qoder ‚Äì $350 \n‚ÄãüöÄ Best Use of Insforge ‚Äì $350 \n‚ÄãüõÝÔ∏è Rules\n‚ÄãPre-planning encouraged: Feel free to come with ideas\, diagrams\, and architecture ready to go. \n‚ÄãTeam Size: Teams of up to 3 people. \n‚ÄãIn-person only: This is a build-and-vibe day in Seattle; remote participation is not available. \n‚ÄãRespect & Inclusion: Mandatory. We are here to create a safe space for bold ideas and collaborative building. \n‚Äãüí° Pro Tip: While you are welcome to use any tools you like\, projects that best demonstrate the synergy between Qoder and Insforge will stand out significantly to the judges. \n‚Äãüß© About the Hosts & Partners\n‚ÄãQoder: The world‚Äôs first Agentic IDE built for real-world software engineering. It acts as an autonomous collaborator that understands entire codebases and executes multi-file edits to help developers ship faster. \n‚ÄãInsforge: An Agent-native Backend Platform that enables AI coding agents to build and operate production-ready backends in seconds\, bridging the gap from prototype to scalable applications. \n‚ÄãB.E.L.L.E Community: A global community of entrepreneurs dedicated to breaking boundaries. We‚Äôve connected over 25\,000 members and supported 600+ startups that have collectively raised over $1 billion.
